ith respect to the classical LES. In particular, the prediction of the\nenstrophy, mean velocity and density distributions and of the energy and\ndensity spectra are substantially improved.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Nov 2012 16:43:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Jun 2013 20:11:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
